{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"n1","type":"text","text":"音频流程对比：compress/audio.rs vs convert/audio.rs","x":40,"y":20,"width":560,"height":70},
		{"id":"n2","type":"text","text":"Compress 入口\ncompress_audio_file(emitter, params)","x":40,"y":130,"width":300,"height":90},
		{"id":"n4","type":"text","text":"Compress 编码参数决策\n1) codec: params.codec -> 输入流codec\n2) sample fmt/rate/layout 通过 media_common 选择\n3) bit_rate/time_base 设置\n4) open encoder + add output stream","x":40,"y":420,"width":340,"height":160},
		{"id":"n5","type":"text","text":"Compress 数据通道\n1) encoder.frame_size > 0 则启用 AudioFifo\n2) 创建 resampler(Context::get)\n3) write_header","x":40,"y":610,"width":320,"height":130},
		{"id":"n6","type":"text","text":"Compress 主循环\npacket -> decoder.receive_frame\nnormalize_decoded_frame\n计算 out_samples","x":40,"y":770,"width":300,"height":120},
		{"id":"n7","type":"text","text":"Compress 重采样\nresampler.run(decoded, resampled)\n若报 Input changed:\n- rebuild_resampler_from_decoded\n- retry run","x":40,"y":920,"width":320,"height":150},
		{"id":"n8","type":"text","text":"Compress 后处理\napply_volume_and_silence\n- 调整音量\n- 可选静音丢帧","x":40,"y":1100,"width":280,"height":120},
		{"id":"n9","type":"text","text":"Compress 编码写出\n分支A: FIFO凑满 frame_size 再 send_frame\n分支B: 直接 send_frame\nreceive_packet -> rescale_ts -> write_interleaved\n按 pts_counter 发进度","x":40,"y":1250,"width":360,"height":170},
		{"id":"n10","type":"text","text":"Compress 收尾\n1) FIFO remaining 发送尾帧\n2) encoder.send_eof + drain packets\n3) write_trailer\n4) 组装 AudioCompressionReport(MediaDetails)","x":40,"y":1450,"width":360,"height":160},
		{"id":"n11","type":"text","text":"Convert 入口\nconvert_audio(emitter, params)","x":560,"y":130,"width":300,"height":90},
		{"id":"n12","type":"text","text":"Convert 参数解析\n1) resolve_format\n2) map_codec_name(含平台/格式映射)\n3) resolve_audio_tracks(可多音轨)\n4) AMR 特殊约束(sample_rate/channels)","x":560,"y":250,"width":360,"height":150},
		{"id":"n13","type":"text","text":"Convert 初始化\n1) ensure_ffmpeg_init + unique output\n2) duration\n3) 打开 ictx/octx\n4) 收集输入音轨索引","x":560,"y":430,"width":330,"height":140},
		{"id":"n14","type":"text","text":"Convert 快路径判断\ntry_stream_copy_audio:\n- 参数未改动\n- codec 与输入一致\n- 无重复映射\n满足则直接 remux","x":560,"y":600,"width":320,"height":140},
		{"id":"n15","type":"text","text":"Convert 快路径执行\nadd_stream(copy) -> write_header\npacket 直接转时间基后写出\nwrite_trailer + complete","x":930,"y":600,"width":300,"height":130},
		{"id":"n17","type":"text","text":"Convert 主循环\n按 stream.index 分发到对应 processor.process_packet\n内部含 Input changed 重建重采样器逻辑\n周期性进度上报","x":560,"y":940,"width":360,"height":150},
		{"id":"n19","type":"text","text":"核心差异\n1) Compress: 单最佳音轨 + 一体化流程\n2) Convert: 可多音轨，支持 stream-copy 快路径\n3) Convert 编码/重采样细节下沉到 AudioTrackProcessor","x":960,"y":860,"width":360,"height":150},
		{"id":"n20","type":"text","text":"易出错点\n1) 编码器可用性(如 libmp3lame 不在构建中)\n2) 输入帧参数变化触发 Input changed\n3) MP3/MF 等编码器对尾帧、采样率/码率限制\n4) 输出容器与编码器不匹配","x":960,"y":1040,"width":360,"height":160},
		{"id":"n16","type":"text","text":"Convert 转码路径初始化\n为每条 resolved track 创建 AudioTrackProcessor\n(内部完成 decoder/encoder/resampler/FIFO/参数协商)","x":560,"y":770,"width":360,"height":130},
		{"id":"n18","type":"text","text":"Convert 收尾\nfor each processor.finish\nwrite_trailer\n组装 AudioConversionReport\n(包含每条输出流 summary)","x":580,"y":1220,"width":340,"height":140},
		{"id":"n3","type":"text","text":"Compress 初始化\n1) ensure_ffmpeg_init\n2) ensure_unique_output_path\n3) 打开 ictx/octx\n4) best(audio) + decoder","x":40,"y":260,"width":320,"height":140}
	],
